      <title>加纳与国际货币基金组织就 3.6 亿美元资金达成工作人员级协议</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-04/ghana-reaches-staff-level-deal-with-imf-for-another-360-million</link>
